[Java program to check even or odd number](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/java-program-to-find-even-or-odd/)

Letâ€™s learn java program to check even or odd number.

import java.util.Scanner;
public class FindEvenOrOdd
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      int a;
      Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
      System.out.println("Please enter a number to check even or odd: ");
      a = sc.nextInt();
      if(a % 2 == 0)
      {
         System.out.println("Entered number is an even number.");
      }
      else
      {
         System.out.println("Entered number is an odd number.");
      }
      sc.close();
   }
}


Output:

Please enter a number to check even or odd: 5
Entered number is an odd number.
